Rick Gomez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rick_Gomez 0 For the actor from Philippines, see Richard Gomez.Richard Harper "Rick" Gomez (born June 1, 1972) is an American actor and voice actor. He is known for portraying Technician 4th Grade George Luz in the HBO television miniseries Band of Brothers, and as "Endless Mike" Hellstrom in the Nickelodeon TV series The Adventures of Pete and Pete. He is the older brother of actor Joshua Gomez. For the_actor from Philippines , see Richard_Gomez.Richard_Harper_"_Rick_"_Gomez ( born June_1_,_1972 ) is an_American_actor_and_voice_actor .
